23:32.333 --> 23:33.500
♪ Try to tell you stop... ♪

23:33.500 --> 23:38.166
If ever you want to go
to a meeting or whatever...

23:38.166 --> 23:40.583
Um, yeah.

23:40.583 --> 23:42.625
Sure, maybe.

23:44.083 --> 23:45.333
Okay, cool.

23:45.333 --> 23:47.125
Just let me know.

23:49.000 --> 23:51.000
Cool.

